snippet: Citing back spasms and pain, Tiger Woods withdrew Tuesday from the Arnold Palmer Invitational, his last scheduled tuneup before the Masters.
abstract: Tiger Woods, citing back spasms and pain, withdraws from the Arnold Palmer Invitational, imperiling his bid for a fifth Masters victory in less than a month.
lead_paragraph: Citing back spasms and pain, Tiger Woods withdrew Tuesday from the Arnold Palmer Invitational, his last scheduled tuneup before the Masters.

headline.main: Bad Back Forces Woods From Palmer Event
headline.print_headline: Bad Back Forces Woods From Palmer Event
